22
00:01:35,380 --> 00:01:40,900
♪Together, another journey awaits♪

23
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:50,020
[The Blood of Youth]

24
00:01:50,250 --> 00:01:52,970
[Episode 14]

25
00:02:02,740 --> 00:02:03,220
Father,

26
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:05,580
I remember a statement

27
00:02:05,780 --> 00:02:06,820
made to me by a master.

28
00:02:07,780 --> 00:02:08,420
Youths

29
00:02:09,060 --> 00:02:10,100
must have their own martial arts world.

30
00:02:11,900 --> 00:02:12,500
Therefore,

31
00:02:14,980 --> 00:02:15,820
I cannot

32
00:02:17,540 --> 00:02:18,420
accept this token.

33
00:02:20,740 --> 00:02:21,580
Father, I'm sorry.

34
00:02:23,980 --> 00:02:24,820
So, you don't like it?

35
00:02:25,420 --> 00:02:26,660
You think I want to give it to you?

36
00:02:26,900 --> 00:02:27,540
Goodness.

37
00:02:27,700 --> 00:02:28,140
Come on.

38
00:02:28,140 --> 00:02:29,740
Let's not talk about the token.

39
00:02:30,060 --> 00:02:31,580
Let's talk about Xiao Chuhe.

40
00:02:31,940 --> 00:02:32,780
Where were we just now?

41
00:02:33,180 --> 00:02:33,940
-That Xiao Chuhe...
-Father!

42
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:37,100
Didn't you just say

43
00:02:37,940 --> 00:02:40,740
that you are going to find someone
you acknowledge

44
00:02:41,140 --> 00:02:43,020
and protect him?

45
00:02:43,140 --> 00:02:45,380
What do you think about Xiao Se?

46
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:49,260
Acknowledgment and protection?

47
00:02:50,540 --> 00:02:51,580
I don't think such terms

48
00:02:52,100 --> 00:02:53,660
are meant for us.

49
00:02:54,340 --> 00:02:56,300
You just don't want to admit it.

50
00:02:57,300 --> 00:02:57,780
All right now.

51
00:02:57,980 --> 00:02:59,300
Go to Xiao Se

52
00:02:59,460 --> 00:03:00,700
and return the favor

53
00:03:00,940 --> 00:03:01,900
to him.

54
00:03:02,100 --> 00:03:03,340
Father!

55
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:08,020
I've known Miss Ruoyi for a long time.

56
00:03:08,620 --> 00:03:10,020
But it was my first time
chatting with her this long.

57
00:03:10,540 --> 00:03:12,140
Have you finished reading "Late Snow"

58
00:03:12,380 --> 00:03:13,260
given to you by Scholarly Sword Deity?

59
00:03:13,900 --> 00:03:14,980
That book is boring.

60
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:16,900
I was sleepy just after reading a few lines.

61
00:03:17,180 --> 00:03:17,860
It's no fun.

62
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:18,540
I don't like that book.

63
00:03:18,940 --> 00:03:19,660
If so, what kind of book

64
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:20,580
do you like?

65
00:03:21,140 --> 00:03:22,060
Naturally, I like books

66
00:03:22,340 --> 00:03:23,980
about wanderers in the martial arts world

67
00:03:24,260 --> 00:03:25,500
and heroes on the battlefield.

68
00:03:25,700 --> 00:03:26,340
For example,

69
00:03:26,860 --> 00:03:27,660
the story of Baiyu Sword Deity

70
00:03:27,980 --> 00:03:29,980
conquering Tianqi by himself.

71
00:03:30,620 --> 00:03:32,340
I will never get tired of it.

72
00:03:32,540 --> 00:03:33,380
The story of Baiyu Sword Deity

73
00:03:33,540 --> 00:03:34,860
conquering Tianqi City?

74
00:03:36,820 --> 00:03:37,540
Xiao Se,

75
00:03:38,380 --> 00:03:39,980
why do you have a weird expression

76
00:03:40,180 --> 00:03:41,180
whenever I mention Tianqi City?

77
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:42,940
If I'm not mistaken,

78
00:03:43,620 --> 00:03:44,940
your hometown should be Tianqi.

79
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:49,100
I don't have a hometown.

80
00:03:50,060 --> 00:03:50,700
You're mistaken.

81
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:52,940
Everyone has a hometown.

82
00:03:53,580 --> 00:03:54,620
Don't tell me you were born

83
00:03:54,780 --> 00:03:55,540
from a rock?

84
00:03:57,780 --> 00:03:59,900
So, what's hometown to you?

85
00:04:00,900 --> 00:04:01,940
Isn't it obvious?

86
00:04:02,820 --> 00:04:03,860
Hometown?

87
00:04:04,300 --> 00:04:05,700
It's a place that you're destined to return to

88
00:04:06,180 --> 00:04:07,260
no matter

89
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:08,380
how far you go

90
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:09,780
or how long

91
00:04:09,780 --> 00:04:11,260
you are away.

92
00:04:14,180 --> 00:04:15,820
A place that we're destined to return to?

93
00:04:19,900 --> 00:04:20,620
You're right.

94
00:04:21,700 --> 00:04:23,300
My hometown is Tianqi City.

95
00:04:24,620 --> 00:04:25,380
It's a place

96
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:28,140
that I'm destined to return to.

97
00:04:44,060 --> 00:04:44,820
Lord Bai said

98
00:04:45,260 --> 00:04:46,180
he is taking you with him

99
00:04:46,180 --> 00:04:47,300
under an imperial order.

100
00:04:48,220 --> 00:04:48,820
However, judging from him

101
00:04:48,820 --> 00:04:50,140
still being here,

102
00:04:51,660 --> 00:04:53,060
I think you've rejected him.

103
00:04:56,260 --> 00:04:57,340
If so, Third City Lord,

104
00:04:59,100 --> 00:05:00,540
do you think I should reject him?

105
00:05:01,460 --> 00:05:02,140
I don't know

106
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:03,940
what he offered,

107
00:05:04,940 --> 00:05:06,060
but judging from the way he looked,

108
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:08,260
there should be

109
00:05:09,220 --> 00:05:10,140
a condition

110
00:05:10,140 --> 00:05:11,900
that would leave many people in awe.

111
00:05:12,340 --> 00:05:12,900
That's right.

112
00:05:14,020 --> 00:05:14,660
However, there's also a reason

113
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:15,900
that I must reject him.

114
00:05:19,460 --> 00:05:20,780
Third City Lord, do you think

115
00:05:21,220 --> 00:05:21,700
I should

116
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:22,660
return with him?

117
00:05:24,140 --> 00:05:25,700
I understand your persistence.

118
00:05:26,260 --> 00:05:27,140
However, in my opinion,

119
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:28,220
if you return to Tianqi

120
00:05:28,220 --> 00:05:29,540
right now,

121
00:05:29,980 --> 00:05:30,900
many issues

122
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:32,250
will be simplified.

123
00:05:32,780 --> 00:05:33,540
It's beneficial to you,

124
00:05:34,140 --> 00:05:35,100
to your father,

125
00:05:35,380 --> 00:05:36,700
and to that incident

126
00:05:37,460 --> 00:05:38,660
in the past.

127
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:39,900
That's right.

128
00:05:40,780 --> 00:05:41,580
Father has already

129
00:05:41,580 --> 00:05:42,380
made a huge compromise.

130
00:05:43,460 --> 00:05:44,340
With his personality,

131
00:05:45,220 --> 00:05:47,140
this is already the extent of his leniency.

132
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:48,780
I heard that Lord Bai

133
00:05:48,780 --> 00:05:49,980
gave you three days.

134
00:05:50,860 --> 00:05:51,380
What's wrong?

135
00:05:52,700 --> 00:05:53,740
Third City Lord, are you also going

136
00:05:53,740 --> 00:05:55,220
to persuade me on his behalf?

137
00:05:57,260 --> 00:05:58,340
I, Sikong Changfeng,

138
00:05:58,580 --> 00:05:59,460
never persuade anyone

139
00:05:59,460 --> 00:06:00,380
on anyone's behalf.

140
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:02,020
I just think

141
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:04,580
that this is a great time

142
00:06:05,820 --> 00:06:08,260
for you to return to Tianqi.

143
00:06:10,020 --> 00:06:10,780
Of course I know that.

144
00:06:11,820 --> 00:06:12,220
All right then.

145
00:06:13,580 --> 00:06:14,820
I'll stop bothering you.

146
00:06:19,180 --> 00:06:19,620
By the way,

147
00:06:20,460 --> 00:06:21,180
what do you think

148
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:23,300
about my daughter?

149
00:06:26,700 --> 00:06:27,420
She's proficient with a spear.

150
00:06:28,100 --> 00:06:29,180
She's inherited your skills.

151
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:31,980
Who asked you about her spear skills?

152
00:06:32,540 --> 00:06:33,260
I'm talking about

153
00:06:33,900 --> 00:06:34,820
her looks.

154
00:06:37,700 --> 00:06:38,380
Her looks?

155
00:06:39,660 --> 00:06:40,780
She inherited her mother's looks.

156
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:43,020
What about her personality?

157
00:06:46,180 --> 00:06:47,100
As for her personality,

158
00:06:48,540 --> 00:06:49,260
it makes her unique.

159
00:06:50,060 --> 00:06:51,100
However, she's pretty special.

160
00:07:03,420 --> 00:07:04,020
(If you return)

161
00:07:04,020 --> 00:07:05,180
(to Tianqi right now,)

162
00:07:05,820 --> 00:07:06,740
(many issues)

163
00:07:06,900 --> 00:07:07,980
(will be simplified.)

164
00:07:08,540 --> 00:07:09,140
(It's beneficial to you,)

165
00:07:09,860 --> 00:07:10,660
(to your father,)

166
00:07:11,220 --> 00:07:12,780
(and to that incident)

167
00:07:13,300 --> 00:07:14,540
(in the past.)

168
00:07:16,370 --> 00:07:17,340
Three days, huh?

169
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:51,900
Wuxin,

170
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:54,740
why are you always here

171
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:55,780
whenever I feel troubled?

172
00:08:00,300 --> 00:08:01,420
Mr. Xiao, that means

173
00:08:02,020 --> 00:08:02,900
you still trust me.

174
00:08:04,220 --> 00:08:05,020
When you're troubled,

175
00:08:05,700 --> 00:08:06,860
you will only feel at ease

176
00:08:07,580 --> 00:08:08,900
when you see your bosom friend.

177
00:08:11,380 --> 00:08:12,900
You're still as narcissistic as always,

178
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:15,260
even in my dreams.

179
00:08:17,580 --> 00:08:18,300
Mr. Xiao,

180
00:08:19,380 --> 00:08:20,140
may I know

181
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:21,260
what is troubling you?

182
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:24,100
It's something I've pondered over

183
00:08:24,780 --> 00:08:26,340
and persevered for a long time.

184
00:08:28,340 --> 00:08:29,500
Sometimes, it's unnecessary

185
00:08:30,300 --> 00:08:31,140
to persevere.

186
00:08:31,900 --> 00:08:32,740
Maybe you'll go farther

187
00:08:33,740 --> 00:08:34,820
if you take another path.

188
00:08:36,060 --> 00:08:36,900
That's what you think too?

189
00:08:38,140 --> 00:08:39,420
But sometimes, it's different.

190
00:08:40,900 --> 00:08:41,860
People in the world think

191
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:43,100
that they must persevere

192
00:08:43,780 --> 00:08:44,460
even if isn't worth it.

193
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:46,500
They think that they should persevere

194
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:47,900
even if there's no hope

195
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:49,780
and that they should persevere

196
00:08:50,180 --> 00:08:51,060
until death.

197
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:52,660
This is quite rare,

198
00:08:53,420 --> 00:08:55,180
but judging from your character,

199
00:08:55,900 --> 00:08:56,660
I'm sure you'll encounter things like these.

200
00:08:58,220 --> 00:08:58,820
Wuxin.

201
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:02,180
Have I resolved your doubts?

202
00:09:03,540 --> 00:09:04,260
What a joke.

203
00:09:05,420 --> 00:09:06,540
I said I was troubled.

204
00:09:07,940 --> 00:09:09,460
I didn't say that I had any doubts.

205
00:09:16,180 --> 00:09:17,740
Lord Bai, how long have you been

206
00:09:18,180 --> 00:09:18,940
staying in Xueyue City?

207
00:09:20,020 --> 00:09:21,100
Counting the day I came,

208
00:09:21,700 --> 00:09:22,660
today's already the fourth day.

209
00:09:24,100 --> 00:09:25,580
Lord Bai, is Xueyue City as interesting

210
00:09:25,580 --> 00:09:26,420
as what you've heard?

211
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:28,180
It's plainer

212
00:09:28,740 --> 00:09:29,540
than what I'd imagined.

213
00:09:30,100 --> 00:09:30,940
Xueyue City

214
00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:32,180
is actually

215
00:09:32,300 --> 00:09:33,340
an ordinary city.

216
00:09:33,980 --> 00:09:35,660
It's just that martial artists

217
00:09:35,980 --> 00:09:37,900
love to adorn it with their own special meanings.

218
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:39,220
However,

219
00:09:39,860 --> 00:09:41,340
it's also special

220
00:09:41,820 --> 00:09:42,420
due to

221
00:09:42,940 --> 00:09:44,180
how plain it is.

222
00:09:45,380 --> 00:09:46,220
Xueyue City

223
00:09:46,580 --> 00:09:47,420
was built by several

224
00:09:47,620 --> 00:09:48,700
martial arts masters

225
00:09:48,900 --> 00:09:50,500
as a shelter from the world a century ago.

226
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:51,500
However,

227
00:09:51,620 --> 00:09:53,220
too many people are paying attention to it now.

228
00:09:53,580 --> 00:09:54,340
It has gone against

229
00:09:54,460 --> 00:09:56,020
the initial goals of our predecessors.

230
00:09:57,180 --> 00:09:58,140
No one can avoid the world entirely

231
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:00,380
if you live in the world.

232
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:02,260
Back then,

233
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:03,500
when you were still the Vermilion Bird,

234
00:10:03,860 --> 00:10:04,700
you razed half of Tianqi

235
00:10:05,140 --> 00:10:06,700
to the ground with your spear.

236
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:10,460
That was all in the past.

237
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:11,940
Since then,

238
00:10:12,740 --> 00:10:14,220
I think it's been around two decades

239
00:10:14,300 --> 00:10:15,540
since you returned to Tianqi.

240
00:10:16,860 --> 00:10:17,420
Lord Bai,

241
00:10:17,940 --> 00:10:19,180
are you asking me

242
00:10:19,860 --> 00:10:21,020
if I will support Xiao Se

243
00:10:21,020 --> 00:10:22,300
just like how I supported

244
00:10:22,900 --> 00:10:23,860
your father back then?

245
00:10:24,620 --> 00:10:25,380
I dare not say so.

246
00:10:26,220 --> 00:10:27,220
Actually, I've never

247
00:10:27,380 --> 00:10:28,460
supported your father before.

248
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:31,660
Lord Langya

249
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:34,060
was the only person I supported.

250
00:10:37,020 --> 00:10:37,460
What's wrong?

251
00:10:38,380 --> 00:10:39,220
Do I sound like

252
00:10:39,220 --> 00:10:40,620
a rebel to you?

253
00:10:41,420 --> 00:10:41,940
That's right.

254
00:10:42,260 --> 00:10:43,140
But I've said it already.

255
00:10:43,820 --> 00:10:45,180
You can complain to your father.

256
00:10:45,580 --> 00:10:46,540
He's not daring enough to make comments

257
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:48,140
because that's the truth.

258
00:10:48,460 --> 00:10:48,980
It's just like

259
00:10:49,220 --> 00:10:50,300
I have an answer

260
00:10:50,500 --> 00:10:51,740
to your previous question.

261
00:10:52,660 --> 00:10:53,340
Yes.

262
00:10:54,260 --> 00:10:55,580
I just didn't expect you

263
00:10:56,340 --> 00:10:57,420
to have such

264
00:10:57,900 --> 00:10:58,900
a resolute answer.

265
00:10:59,900 --> 00:11:02,060
I've always been a decisive man.

266
00:11:02,660 --> 00:11:03,820
Although I said I supported him,

267
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:04,540
I wasn't saying

268
00:11:04,540 --> 00:11:05,900
that I would support him
in robbing things of others.

269
00:11:06,420 --> 00:11:08,820
I was saying that I would support
every decision he made.

270
00:11:09,300 --> 00:11:11,140
Just like how he's working as an accountant

271
00:11:11,380 --> 00:11:12,540
in Xueyue City right now.

272
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:14,540
Even if he's going to do that
for the rest of his life,

273
00:11:15,060 --> 00:11:16,340
I will support him.

274
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:20,100
After all, Xiao Se is unparalleled

275
00:11:21,340 --> 00:11:22,700
when it comes to accounting.

276
00:11:26,700 --> 00:11:27,780
I understand now.

277
00:11:28,260 --> 00:11:30,860
[Xiaoqing Pavilion]

278
00:11:38,260 --> 00:11:38,820
Chuhe,

279
00:11:39,940 --> 00:11:40,980
time's up.

280
00:11:44,420 --> 00:11:44,940
Doesn't that mean

281
00:11:44,940 --> 00:11:46,100
you're returning tomorrow?

282
00:11:47,220 --> 00:11:48,060
I will leave

283
00:11:48,940 --> 00:11:49,780
after getting your answer.

284
00:11:53,940 --> 00:11:55,460
Restoring my status as a prince,

285
00:11:57,540 --> 00:11:59,140
and I'll be given the title of Lord Yong'an?

286
00:11:59,740 --> 00:12:00,620
Those conditions

287
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:02,980
are tempting indeed.

288
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:05,060
You and I understand our father's temper well.

289
00:12:06,060 --> 00:12:07,380
He has already made a huge compromise

