586
00:24:03,100 --> 00:24:05,300
He's our foster father indeed.

587
00:24:07,860 --> 00:24:08,860
Our foster father?

588
00:24:09,940 --> 00:24:11,900
Brother, you're deceptive

589
00:24:12,500 --> 00:24:13,420
