599
00:24:33,020 --> 00:24:34,460
That's not a good choice.

600
00:24:35,260 --> 00:24:36,940
After all, there's no pleasant memory

601
00:24:37,940 --> 00:24:39,500
between us.

602
00:24:40,660 --> 00:24:41,380
However,

603
00:24:42,540 --> 00:24:43,860
taking over the world

604
00:24:45,340 --> 00:24:46,460
