628
00:25:39,620 --> 00:25:41,380
I need you to steal him

629
00:25:42,180 --> 00:25:43,060
or kill him.

630
00:25:44,140 --> 00:25:44,860
Don't tell me

631
00:25:46,500 --> 00:25:47,540
