667
00:27:12,740 --> 00:27:13,340
Remember,

668
00:27:13,860 --> 00:27:14,900
Xiao Se mustn't die.

669
00:27:15,740 --> 00:27:16,780
That's my bottom line.

670
00:27:29,060 --> 00:27:29,660
